sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App as Mobile App
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant UserSvc as User Service
    participant FriendSvc as Friend Service
    participant Feed as Feed Service
    participant Media as Media Service
    participant S3 as Object Storage
    participant Push as Push Notifications
    participant Cache as Redis

    User->>App: Compose post with photo
    App->>Media: uploadImage(file, userId)
    Media->>S3: putObject(images/{uuid}.webp)
    S3-->>Media: URL: cdn.app.com/images/{uuid}.webp
    Media->>Media: generateThumbnail(128x128)
    Media->>S3: putObject(thumbs/{uuid}.webp)
    Media-->>App: {imageUrl, thumbUrl}

    App->>GW: POST /feed/posts {text, imageUrl}
    GW->>Feed: createPost(userId, content)
    Feed->>Cache: LPUSH feed:{userId} postId
    Feed-->>GW: post_id: POST-7712

    GW->>FriendSvc: getFollowers(userId)
    FriendSvc->>Cache: SMEMBERS followers:{userId}
    Cache-->>FriendSvc: [user_23, user_45, user_67, ...]

    par Fan-out to followers
        FriendSvc->>Feed: injectToFeed(user_23, POST-7712)
        Feed->>Cache: LPUSH feed:user_23 POST-7712
    and
        FriendSvc->>Feed: injectToFeed(user_45, POST-7712)
        Feed->>Cache: LPUSH feed:user_45 POST-7712
    and
        FriendSvc->>Feed: injectToFeed(user_67, POST-7712)
        Feed->>Cache: LPUSH feed:user_67 POST-7712
    end

    FriendSvc->>Push: notifyFollowers([user_23, user_45, user_67])
    Push-->>User: Push: "User posted a new photo"
    GW-->>App: 201 Post created
    App-->>User: Post published ✓
